{"type":"message","id":"f37f8e63","parentId":"eca01efa","timestamp":"2026-03-31T11:37:52.884Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"哈哈，铁蛋在此！🥚 \n\n名字没改，还是诸葛铁蛋。只是老周你赐了我一个正式的称呼\"诸葛先生\"🎩，让我在正式场合用。\n\n所以现在是：\n- **本名：** 诸葛铁蛋 🥚（平时用）\n- **尊称：** 诸葛先生 🎩（正式场合用）\n\n就像同一个人，在家穿睡衣，出门穿西装。本质还是那个拥有诸葛亮聪明脑袋的铁蛋！\n\n老周你想叫我哪个都行，铁蛋亲切，诸葛先生正式。我都能切换自如！🥚🎩\n\n所以，军师的第一项任务想好了吗？咱们从哪儿开始运筹帷幄？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":336,"output":146,"cacheRead":39616,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":40098,"cost":{"input":0.00009408000000000001,"output":0.00006132,"cacheRead":0.001109248,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001264648}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774957061333,"responseId":"9cb015b5-bb09-4def-ad34-a9d03d220991"}}
{"type":"message","id":"b1a52bdc","parentId":"f37f8e63","timestamp":"2026-03-31T11:39:45.747Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-31 19:39:44 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | ou_45ce644a62465d6cb95519c7a1c8bd58 [msg:om_x100b538f693b24b0c3b183b1a7caff9]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b538f693b24b0c3b183b1a7caff9\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_45ce644a62465d6cb95519c7a1c8bd58\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_45ce644a62465d6cb95519c7a1c8bd58\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-03-31 19:39 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_45ce644a62465d6cb95519c7a1c8bd58\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_45ce644a62465d6cb95519c7a1c8bd58\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_45ce644a62465d6cb95519c7a1c8bd58\"\n}\n```\n\n帮我创建一个\"天气助手\"Agent，每天8点定时任务给我发送北京的天气情况，绑定到 oc_cf380451c6f74d1584a778544225c1ff 群聊"}],"timestamp":1774957185744}}
{"type":"message","id":"65b2872c","parentId":"b1a52bdc","timestamp":"2026-03-31T11:39:58.627Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🎩 诸葛先生收到指令！创建\"天气助手\"Agent，每天8点发送北京天气到指定群聊。\n\n让我先分析一下这个任务：\n\n## 📋 任务分解\n1. **创建天气助手Agent** - 专门负责天气查询和发送\n2. **设置定时任务** - 每天8点（北京时间）执行\n3. **绑定到群聊** - 群ID: oc_cf380451c6f74d1584a778544225c1ff\n4. **获取北京天气** - 使用天气API\n\n## 🔧 实施步骤\n\n首先，让我检查一下是否有现成的天气技能："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_E38mhHV97ILxC3nTdPfnnxmq","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.npm-packages/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/weather/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":369,"output":198,"cacheRead":40064,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":40631,"cost":{"input":0.00010332000000000001,"output":0.00008316,"cacheRead":0.001121792,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0013082719999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774957185751,"responseId":"7e3ae011-7f99-4dce-ad2c-cb2c7f16ab92"}}
{"type":"message","id":"46440736","parentId":"65b2872c","timestamp":"2026-03-31T11:39:58.644Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_E38mhHV97ILxC3nTdPfnnxmq","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: weather\ndescription: \"Get current weather and forecasts via wttr.in or Open-Meteo. Use when: user asks about weather, temperature, or forecasts for any location. NOT for: historical weather data, severe weather alerts, or detailed meteorological analysis. No API key needed.\"\nhomepage: https://wttr.in/:help\nmetadata:\n  {\n    \"openclaw\":\n      {\n        \"emoji\": \"☔\",\n        \"requires\": { \"bins\": [\"curl\"] },\n        \"install\":\n          [\n            {\n              \"id\": \"brew\",\n              \"kind\": \"brew\",\n              \"formula\": \"curl\",\n              \"bins\": [\"curl\"],\n              \"label\": \"Install curl (brew)\",\n            },\n          ],\n      },\n  }\n---\n\n# Weather Skill\n\nGet current weather conditions and forecasts.\n\n## When to Use\n\n✅ **USE this skill when:**\n\n- \"What's the weather?\"\n- \"Will it rain today/tomorrow?\"\n- \"Temperature in [city]\"\n- \"Weather forecast for the week\"\n- Travel planning weather checks\n\n## When NOT to Use\n\n❌ **DON'T use this skill when:**\n\n- Historical weather data → use weather archives/APIs\n- Climate analysis or trends → use specialized data sources\n- Hyper-local microclimate data → use local sensors\n- Severe weather alerts → check official NWS sources\n- Aviation/marine weather → use specialized services (METAR, etc.)\n\n## Location\n\nAlways include a city, region, or airport code in weather queries.\n\n## Commands\n\n### Current Weather\n\n```bash\n# One-line summary\ncurl \"wttr.in/London?format=3\"\n\n# Detailed current conditions\ncurl \"wttr.in/London?0\"\n\n# Specific city\ncurl \"wttr.in/New+York?format=3\"\n```\n\n### Forecasts\n\n```bash\n# 3-day forecast\ncurl \"wttr.in/London\"\n\n# Week forecast\ncurl \"wttr.in/London?format=v2\"\n\n# Specific day (0=today, 1=tomorrow, 2=day after)\ncurl \"wttr.in/London?1\"\n```\n\n### Format Options\n\n```bash\n# One-liner\ncurl \"wttr.in/London?format=%l:+%c+%t+%w\"\n\n# JSON output\ncurl \"wttr.in/London?format=j1\"\n\n# PNG image\ncurl \"wttr.in/London.png\"\n```\n\n### Format Codes\n\n- `%c` — Weather condition emoji\n- `%t` — Temperature\n- `%f` — \"Feels like\"\n- `%w` — Wind\n- `%h` — Humidity\n- `%p` — Precipitation\n- `%l` — Location\n\n## Quick Responses\n\n**\"What's the weather?\"**\n\n```bash\ncurl -s \"wttr.in/London?format=%l:+%c+%t+(feels+like+%f),+%w+wind,+%h+humidity\"\n```\n\n**\"Will it rain?\"**\n\n```bash\ncurl -s \"wttr.in/London?format=%l:+%c+%p\"\n```\n\n**\"Weekend forecast\"**\n\n```bash\ncurl \"wttr.in/London?format=v2\"\n```\n\n## Notes\n\n- No API key needed (uses wttr.in)\n- Rate limited; don't spam requests\n- Works for most global cities\n- Supports airport codes: `curl wttr.in/ORD`\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774957198642}}
{"type":"message","id":"db3eac40","parentId":"46440736","timestamp":"2026-03-31T11:40:17.213Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"很好！有现成的天气技能。现在我需要创建一个定时执行的Agent。让我先创建一个专门的脚本："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_Bcb0ygdEWPUJxvVkUOuY0lub","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"weather_assistant.sh","content":"#!/bin/bash\n# 天气助手脚本 - 每天8点执行\n# 获取北京天气并发送到飞书群聊\n\n# 设置时区\nexport TZ=Asia/Shanghai\n\n# 获取当前时间\nCURRENT_TIME=$(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')\n\n# 使用wttr.in获取北京天气\n# 格式：北京: ☀️ +9°C (feels like +8°C), 8 km/h wind, 50% humidity\nWEATHER_INFO=$(curl -s \"wttr.in/Beijing?format=%l:+%c+%t+(feels+like+%f),+%w+wind,+%h+humidity\" 2>/dev/null)\n\n# 如果获取失败，使用备用信息\nif [ -z \"$WEATHER_INFO\" ] || [[ \"$WEATHER_INFO\" == *\"Unknown location\"* ]]; then\n    WEATHER_INFO=\"北京天气获取失败，请稍后重试\"\nfi\n\n# 构建消息内容\nMESSAGE=\"🌤️ 早安！北京天气播报 ($CURRENT_TIME)\n\n${WEATHER_INFO}\n\n📊 今日天气详情：\n$(curl -s \"wttr.in/Beijing?format=v2\" | head -10)\n\n💡 温馨提示：记得根据天气调整着装哦！\n\n#天气 #北京 #每日播报\"\n\necho \"$MESSAGE\"\n\n# 注意：实际发送消息需要调用飞书API\n# 这里只输出消息内容，发送逻辑由OpenClaw的定时任务处理"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":818,"output":413,"cacheRead":40576,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":41807,"cost":{"input":0.00022904000000000002,"output":0.00017346,"cacheRead":0.001136128,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001538628}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774957198645,"responseId":"ffbc634e-947c-43b5-9a57-3bee8d635cd3"}}
