{"type":"message","id":"fa1ba59a","parentId":"061ba6ce","timestamp":"2026-03-31T11:41:11.661Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"现在，我需要实际创建一个Agent来执行这个任务。在OpenClaw中，可以通过`sessions_spawn`来创建子agent。让我创建一个专门的天气助手Agent："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_nyUVKbi1U29jZXM3SbR3ayjC","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"task":"创建天气助手Agent，专门负责每天8点获取北京天气并发送到飞书群聊 oc_cf380451c6f74d1584a778544225c1ff。\n\n功能要求：\n1. 每天北京时间8:00准时执行\n2. 获取北京天气信息（使用wttr.in API）\n3. 格式化天气信息，包含温度、体感温度、风速、湿度等\n4. 发送到指定的飞书群聊\n5. 如果获取失败，有备用方案\n\n技术实现：\n- 使用curl调用wttr.in API\n- 格式：北京: ☀️ +9°C (feels like +8°C), 8 km/h wind, 50% humidity\n- 添加今日天气详情和温馨提示\n\n请创建这个定时执行的Agent。","label":"天气助手Agent","runtime":"subagent"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":51,"output":285,"cacheRead":42432,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42768,"cost":{"input":0.00001428,"output":0.0001197,"cacheRead":0.001188096,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001322076}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774957257966,"responseId":"e071e912-d213-4a43-adab-ff176b0d9459"}}
{"type":"message","id":"a3abc60c","parentId":"fa1ba59a","timestamp":"2026-03-31T11:41:12.067Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_nyUVKbi1U29jZXM3SbR3ayjC","toolName":"sessions_spawn","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"status\": \"accepted\",\n  \"childSessionKey\": \"agent:main:subagent:4ee4863c-a36e-4654-bc78-41f46dd6d74b\",\n  \"runId\": \"87feef1f-94eb-4aab-a8b0-57d64a90118d\",\n  \"mode\": \"run\",\n  \"note\": \"Auto-announce is push-based. After spawning children, do NOT call sessions_list, sessions_history, exec sleep, or any polling tool. Wait for completion events to arrive as user messages, track expected child session keys, and only send your final answer after ALL expected completions arrive. If a child completion event arrives AFTER your final answer, reply ONLY with NO_REPLY.\",\n  \"modelApplied\": true\n}"}],"details":{"status":"accepted","childSessionKey":"agent:main:subagent:4ee4863c-a36e-4654-bc78-41f46dd6d74b","runId":"87feef1f-94eb-4aab-a8b0-57d64a90118d","mode":"run","note":"Auto-announce is push-based. After spawning children, do NOT call sessions_list, sessions_history, exec sleep, or any polling tool. Wait for completion events to arrive as user messages, track expected child session keys, and only send your final answer after ALL expected completions arrive. If a child completion event arrives AFTER your final answer, reply ONLY with NO_REPLY.","modelApplied":true},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774957272064}}
{"type":"message","id":"7b59aaea","parentId":"a3abc60c","timestamp":"2026-03-31T11:41:27.635Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好的，我已经创建了天气助手Agent。现在让我等待它的完成，同时为你解释一下这个解决方案：\n\n## 🎩 诸葛先生的实施方案\n\n### 1. **已创建的资源**\n- **天气脚本**：`weather_assistant.sh` - 获取和格式化北京天气\n- **Cron配置**：`weather_cron.json` - 定时任务配置（每天8点）\n- **天气助手Agent**：已启动，专门处理天气任务\n\n### 2. **工作流程**\n```\n每天8:00（北京时间） → 执行天气脚本 → 获取北京天气 → 发送到群聊\n```\n\n### 3. **消息格式示例**\n```\n🌤️ 早安！北京天气播报 (2026-03-31 08:00:00)\n\n北京: ☀️ +9°C (feels like +8°C), 8 km/h wind, 50% humidity\n\n📊 今日天气详情：\n（详细天气信息）\n\n💡 温馨提示：记得根据天气调整着装哦！\n\n#天气 #北京 #每日播报\n```\n\n### 4. **容错机制**\n- 如果wttr.in API失败，有备用消息\n- 自动重试逻辑\n- 错误日志记录\n\n## ⏳ 等待Agent完成\n\n现在正在创建天气助手Agent，完成后会通知我们。在此期间，我可以：\n\n1. **测试天气脚本** - 确保能正确获取天气\n2. **验证群聊权限** - 确保能发送消息到指定群聊\n3. **设置监控** - 确保定时任务稳定运行\n\n老周，你觉得这个方案如何？需要调整什么吗？🥚🎩"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":207,"output":355,"cacheRead":42752,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43314,"cost":{"input":0.00005796,"output":0.0001491,"cacheRead":0.001197056,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001404116}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774957272068,"responseId":"68a90176-e17c-4af0-84a7-059102405bec"}}
