{"type":"message","id":"d8d948e3","parentId":"584a4142","timestamp":"2026-03-31T11:41:54.024Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"很好！天气脚本工作正常。现在获取到的北京天气是：\n- **温度：** +17°C（体感+17°C）\n- **风速：** ↑12km/h  \n- **湿度：** 39%\n- **天气：** ☀️ 晴天\n\n现在让我检查一下群聊是否存在，以及我们是否有权限发送消息："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_uqbs4LuSBn7TX2iK57oJbQJY","name":"feishu_chat","arguments":{"action":"get","chat_id":"oc_cf380451c6f74d1584a778544225c1ff"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":349,"output":155,"cacheRead":43648,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44152,"cost":{"input":0.00009772,"output":0.0000651,"cacheRead":0.0012221439999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0013849639999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774957302744,"responseId":"76e8bfb7-1b04-4d3c-b1f8-7cb33c22da03"}}
