{"type":"message","id":"112a7a95","parentId":"1e9b2c92","timestamp":"2026-03-31T11:47:31.903Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"JSON解析有点问题，让我修复一下。不过基本功能是正常的。现在最关键的是发送消息的权限。\n\n老周，你点击了授权卡片中的链接了吗？如果点击了，让我再试一次发送测试消息："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_mLlkHh4YjET1qWSmGkmXbeCS","name":"feishu_im_user_message","arguments":{"action":"send","receive_id_type":"chat_id","receive_id":"oc_cf380451c6f74d1584a778544225c1ff","msg_type":"text","content":"{\"text\":\"🧪 测试消息 - 最终测试\\n\\n这是诸葛铁蛋的最终测试消息。如果成功，我们就可以设置定时任务了！\\n\\n测试时间：2026-03-31 19:47\\n\\n#测试 #天气助手\"}"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":152,"output":238,"cacheRead":49856,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":50246,"cost":{"input":0.000042560000000000006,"output":0.00009996,"cacheRead":0.001395968,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001538488}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774957636170,"responseId":"b14e5a32-4ba4-4e0f-95f0-af039a65a95e"}}
