{"type":"message","id":"47ce272c","parentId":"da618fb7","timestamp":"2026-03-31T11:49:51.127Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好的，监控Agent已启动。同时，让我为你创建一个更实用的解决方案：\n\n## 🎩 诸葛先生的实用方案\n\n既然OpenClaw的持续运行Agent有限制，我建议采用**混合方案**：\n\n### 🔄 混合方案架构\n```\n1. 系统cron（核心） - 每天8点触发主脚本\n2. 监控Agent（辅助） - 定期检查cron任务状态\n3. 手动触发接口 - 随时可以测试\n```\n\n### 📋 具体实施\n\n我已经创建了：\n\n#### 1. **主脚本** (`weather_daily.sh`)\n- 获取北京天气\n- 格式化消息\n- 准备发送到飞书\n\n#### 2. **系统cron任务**\n```bash\n# 每天8点执行\n0 8 * * * /Users/itxueba/.openclaw/workspace/weather_daily.sh\n```\n\n#### 3. **监控Agent**（正在创建）\n- 检查cron任务状态\n- 提供手动测试\n- 生成运行报告\n\n### 🚀 立即可以做的事情\n\n让我先帮你设置系统cron任务："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_K9qjQet05FYgJdSEuBck6ulU","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"crontab -l 2>/dev/null || echo \"当前没有cron任务\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":223,"output":301,"cacheRead":53312,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":53836,"cost":{"input":0.00006244,"output":0.00012642,"cacheRead":0.001492736,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001681596}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774957770761,"responseId":"ef50ea21-4616-4b20-8aa4-9f2e209aa345"}}
