{"type":"message","id":"34cc3f95","parentId":"1a7c9864","timestamp":"2026-03-31T11:50:40.445Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"老周，现在我需要你的确认来执行这个cron设置。因为修改cron任务需要权限。\n\n## 🎯 请确认以下操作\n\n### 将要执行的操作\n1. **添加cron任务**：每天8点执行天气脚本\n2. **创建日志文件**：`/tmp/weather_cron.log`\n3. **设置备注**：标明是\"诸葛铁蛋设置\"\n\n### 执行命令\n```bash\nbash /Users/itxueba/.openclaw/workspace/weather_cron_setup.sh\n```\n\n### 预期结果\n- 从明天（4月1日）开始，每天8点自动发送北京天气\n- 可以在`/tmp/weather_cron.log`查看运行日志\n- 可以随时手动测试\n\n老周，你确认要执行这个cron设置吗？如果确认，我就执行。🥚🎩\n\n（同时，监控Agent正在创建中，完成后会提供管理界面）"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":48,"output":204,"cacheRead":54336,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":54588,"cost":{"input":0.00001344,"output":0.00008568,"cacheRead":0.001521408,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001620528}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774957825475,"responseId":"f0be260e-ab1c-4ad1-96ef-acbef92c2b46"}}
