{"type":"message","id":"096a71ff","parentId":"93e51f63","timestamp":"2026-03-31T12:44:09.575Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🎩 **OpenClaw gateway已停止，但权限问题依然存在！**\n\n老周，我刚刚停止了OpenClaw gateway进程（PID: 82319）。现在需要：\n\n## 🔄 **重启OpenClaw的步骤**\n\n### 1. **先处理权限问题**（依然存在）\n**授权链接：** https://open.feishu.cn/app/cli_a938e4a7a6bbdcd1/auth?q=contact%3Acontact.base%3Areadonly&op_from=openapi&token_type=tenant\n\n### 2. **然后启动OpenClaw**\n我需要知道如何启动OpenClaw。通常有几种方式：\n\n**方式A：使用服务命令**\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway start\n```\n\n**方式B：直接运行**\n```bash\nopenclaw-gateway\n```\n\n**方式C：通过npm**\n```bash\nnpx openclaw gateway start\n```\n\n## 🎩 **诸葛先生的建议**\n\n**建议顺序：**\n1. 🔐 **先完成权限授权**（点击上面的链接）\n2. 🔄 **然后启动OpenClaw**（告诉我使用哪个命令）\n\n## 📋 **当前状态**\n- ✅ OpenClaw gateway已停止\n- 🔐 权限问题待解决\n- 🔄 等待重启命令\n\n老周，**请先点击权限授权链接**，然后告诉我：\n1. 授权完成了吗？\n2. 使用什么命令启动OpenClaw？\n\n🥚 **铁蛋等着你的指示！** 🎩"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":316,"output":321,"cacheRead":66304,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":66941,"cost":{"input":0.00008848,"output":0.00013482000000000001,"cacheRead":0.001856512,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002079812}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774961020654,"responseId":"30f4a38f-c9cf-434c-8b64-a9160b84a6b0"}}
