{"type":"message","id":"5b3b6c67","parentId":"25f2dc5a","timestamp":"2026-03-31T13:09:12.432Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"让我检查一下OpenClaw的启动方式。通常工作空间是在启动时指定的。\n\n## 🎯 **切换方案**\n\n### 方案1：重启OpenClaw指定工作空间\n```bash\n# 停止当前gateway\nkill 83485\n\n# 启动时指定workspace-zhuge\n~/.npm-packages/bin/openclaw --workspace /Users/itxueba/.openclaw/workspace-zhuge gateway run\n```\n\n### 方案2：修改当前会话配置\n可能需要修改运行时配置\n\n### 方案3：创建符号链接\n```bash\n# 备份当前workspace\nmv /Users/itxueba/.openclaw/workspace /Users/itxueba/.openclaw/workspace-backup\n\n# 创建指向workspace-zhuge的链接\nln -s /Users/itxueba/.openclaw/workspace-zhuge /Users/itxueba/.openclaw/workspace\n```\n\n## 🎩 **诸葛铁蛋的建议**\n\n**建议使用方案3（符号链接）**，因为：\n1. 最简单直接\n2. 不需要重启OpenClaw\n3. 可以随时切换回来\n\n**让我执行方案3：**"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_lGrQEPhHvW8K6QEKLEo7yzdm","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /Users/itxueba/.openclaw && mv workspace workspace-backup && ln -s workspace-zhuge workspace && echo \"工作空间已切换到 workspace-zhuge\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":79,"output":338,"cacheRead":74304,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":74721,"cost":{"input":0.00002212,"output":0.00014196,"cacheRead":0.002080512,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002244592}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774962513407,"responseId":"34f62032-bc43-4bfa-8aa8-f8aaacef27e4"}}
