{"type":"message","id":"6652ea62","parentId":"01ff0f95","timestamp":"2026-03-31T13:11:50.873Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🦸♀️ **群聊验证通过！**\n\n**群聊信息：**\n- 类型：p2p（私聊）\n- 状态：正常\n- 群主：老周（ou_45ce644a62465d6cb95519c7a1c8bd58）\n- 成员数：0（可能是新建的群）\n\n## 🎯 **绑定方案**\n\n在OpenClaw中，绑定工作空间到群聊通常需要：\n\n### 方案1：修改OpenClaw配置\n```json\n{\n  \"workspace\": \"/Users/itxueba/.openclaw/workspace-zhuge\",\n  \"bindings\": {\n    \"oc_8d0f424e1590f3522dd66fbaef052fb5\": \"workspace-zhuge\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 方案2：创建会话映射\n在群聊中自动加载指定工作空间\n\n### 方案3：使用环境变量\n启动时指定工作空间和绑定关系\n\n## 🎩 **诸葛先生的行动**\n\n**妥妥的！** 让我先检查当前OpenClaw的配置方式："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_qaamnyxFhKeIvlZhlRZhPzZa","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ps aux | grep openclaw | grep -v grep"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":270,"output":294,"cacheRead":75904,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":76468,"cost":{"input":0.00007560000000000001,"output":0.00012348,"cacheRead":0.002125312,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0023243919999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774962671634,"responseId":"7fa7ad0f-c825-4e33-8497-8e878bdfea46"}}
