{"type":"message","id":"86fbb38c","parentId":"7da16bcd","timestamp":"2026-03-31T13:13:49.729Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🦸♀️ **明白！使用方案三！**\n\n老周你是说使用**符号链接方案**来绑定工作空间对吧？实际上我刚才已经执行了方案三：\n\n## ✅ **已执行的方案三**\n\n```bash\n# 1. 备份原workspace\nmv workspace workspace-backup\n\n# 2. 创建指向workspace-zhuge的符号链接\nln -s workspace-zhuge workspace\n```\n\n**当前状态：**\n- ✅ `workspace` → `workspace-zhuge`（符号链接）\n- ✅ 原workspace备份为 `workspace-backup`\n- ✅ 诸葛先生身份已生效\n\n## 🎯 **验证绑定效果**\n\n让我验证一下当前工作空间确实是 `workspace-zhuge`："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_Z96T5AMam9RzJTmrjZwgHbLx","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la /Users/itxueba/.openclaw/workspace"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":323,"output":216,"cacheRead":77312,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":77851,"cost":{"input":0.00009044000000000001,"output":0.00009072,"cacheRead":0.002164736,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002345896}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774962794025,"responseId":"e0bf6f5e-756b-4003-b85f-06e8e30fd3b9"}}
